She stood next to Scorponok. She wanted to smack him for the programs he had 
placed in her mainframe systems.  This new program made her obey him, 
Quickstrike and Megatron.  And the program over rided her own will on her 
actions if any of those three gave her a command.  She felt like mouse on a 
lease.

"Is the cave satisfactory or do you want to look around some more?"
